body.name: Open Chassis Rack PC Test Bench 300W Vertical Test Frame Motherboard Case Metal Frame for PC Motherboard Case ATX/M-ATX/ITX Chassis Bracket (Red)
features: Fully open chassis: This chassis is made of aluminum and thick acrylic boards, which has durable and corrosion-resistant characteristics. This metal frame is skillfully fixed by screws and is very stable

Thermal Performance: It has the characteristics of fully naked heat dissipation, installed in the chassis on the host can be in the operation process of rapid and timely heat dissipation, reduce the damage caused by the host
Compatibility: It is suitable for ITX motherboards, MATX and ATX motherboards. It also supports 7 PCI expansion slots
Install: This chassis is simple, easy to handle, easy to install, and you can install it yourself with all the accessories we offer you
Quality services: If you have any questions, please contact us and we will reply within 24 hours. We will try our best to solve your problems. Provide you with satisfactory products and services
